name: Chicago Golf Galaxy & Tennis Warehouse, Inc.
overview: Whether you’re an avid golf player or a tennis fanatic, you will find everything you will ever need from our broad selection of golfing and tennis products. Golf clubs, tennis racquets, balls, bags, training aids and other related accessories are all available from a number of reputable and leading brands in the sports market. Store owner, Kent Johnstone, first started playing golf about 5 years ago after being introduced to the sport by a colleague during a company outing. Since then, Kent bought his own self of clubs and has acquired membership at a local golf club in his hometown. Now, being an avid golfer, He can be seen regularly at his club, playing and constantly improving his skills at the game. He has also recently introduced his young son, Aaron, to the world of golf and both enjoy having father and son matches from time to time. Aside from golf, Kent also plays tennis to keep fit and is a huge basketball fan.
